### MVP Backend - Teste de Rotas
### Use com REST Client (VS Code Extension) ou Postman

### 1. Health Check
GET http://localhost:3001/health

### 2. Status do Backend
GET http://localhost:3001/

### 3. Upload de Post (substitua o caminho do arquivo)
POST http://localhost:3001/api/upload-post
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="clienteId"

cliente123
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="titulo"

Meu Primeiro Post
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="descricao"

Este é um post de teste
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="test.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./test-image.jpg
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

### 4. Buscar Posts de um Cliente
GET http://localhost:3001/api/posts/cliente123

### 5. Processar Post
POST http://localhost:3001/api/process-post
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "postId": 1,
  "status": "processado",
  "metadata": {
    "processedAt": "2024-01-01T00:00:00.000Z",
    "tags": ["teste", "sucesso"]
  }
}

### 6. Buscar Posts Processados
GET http://localhost:3001/api/posts/cliente123

